 <!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name=viewport content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"><title>宋仲基吴亦凡李易峰霍建华 中韩男星军装PK谁最帅 - 360新闻搜索</title><link type="image/x-icon"rel="shortcut icon"href="/faviconso.ico"><link rel=stylesheet href="http://s8.qhimg.com/static/05e96eb2b81f370b/article.css"><script>var ENV_MONITOR={},WPO={};WPO.data={dcl:[+(new Date)]}</script><script>var $pro = 'm_news', $pid='result_view';</script></head><body class="body_SO"><script>/(mso_app|360newsapp|360 Aphone Browser|QHBrowser)/ig.test(navigator.userAgent)&&(document.body.className+=" notop"),!navigator.userAgent.match(/(i[^;]+\;( ?U;)? CPU.+Mac OS X)/)||(document.body.className+=" ios",document.downUrl="https://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/id990129323")</script>  <header class=header> <a class=back href="javascript:void('back');"></a> <h1 class=logo><a href="/"></a></h1> <dl class=fontsize> <dt> <dd> <a class=subFontSize href="javascript:void('subFontSize');"></a> <a class=addFontSize href="javascript:void('addFontSize');"></a> </dl> </header>   <article id=news> <header> <h1 id="news-title">宋仲基吴亦凡李易峰霍建华 中韩男星军装PK谁最帅 </h1> <p id="source-and-time"><span id=source>人民网江西频道</span><time id=time>2016-03-15 19:51:00</time></p> </header>  <div id="news-body"><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01b416b21c05d532ee.jpg?size=500x333"></p><p class="img-title">持枪的样子简直帅炸天际。</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t015a682fb456fdc319.jpg?size=500x334"></p><p>这样霸气侧漏的出场撩妹也是没sei了。</p><p><a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%B2%E5%9F%BA&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">宋仲基</a>通过电视剧《善良的男人》和电影《狼族少年》跻身一线男演员，在2013年8月时进入江原道春川102连队服兵役。来看看现实生活中宋欧巴军队里的照片:</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t012c748dd31c834676.jpg?size=540x397"></p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t019cfe9391bf9c1088.jpg?size=423x640"></p><p class="img-title">是不是比起电视剧来也毫不逊色呢?</p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t01066320a9161df46d.jpg?size=550x366"></p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t01c7e99ba1e6394778.jpg?size=550x825"></p><p>1993年的小鲜肉俞承浩，曾与尹恩惠共同出演大热韩剧《想你》，这也是他入伍前的最后一部作品。虽然平时的他多少给人奶油小生之感，但是穿上军装后整个人坚毅了许多。</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01182a61cad5f55ea9.jpg?size=540x514"></p><p>东方神起允浩，入伍后剃了平头的他依然十分精神帅气。果然平头是检验帅哥的唯一标准，底子好啥发型都能驾驭。</p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t014372ed5c1e6bbd82.jpg?size=500x750"></p><p>男神玄彬，想当年他入伍的时候有多少妹子伤心欲绝。</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01d9394effd7eacbc3.jpg?size=530x593"></p><p>看这完美侧颜你猜到是哪位韩国男明星了吗?</p><p><img src="http://p35.qhimg.com/t01201203933da4367a.jpg?size=528x591"></p><p>Bingo，答案就是曾出演过《王的男人》<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《我的女孩》</a>《夜行书生》的李准基。他的美貌令女人都汗颜。</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t010f880ae879d9123d.jpg?size=430x646"></p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t0110dd9ff998f94583.jpg?size=430x644"></p><p>曾经与乔妹合作过<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E9%82%A3%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%E9%A3%8E%E5%9C%A8%E5%90%B9%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《那年冬天风在吹》</a>的赵寅成，穿上军装也是帅帅哒。</p><p><img src="http://p35.qhimg.com/t011deb19408ac3a9c2.jpg?size=406x517"></p><p>Super Junior金希澈，入伍的他也展示了自己罕见的平头造型。</p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t018df653bef015541b.jpg?size=322x500"></p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t01807d7c7fcd259d37.jpg?size=520x780"></p><p>拐走了我大中国亦菲女神的宋承宪欧巴。</p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t01e454eae66ceb07d7.jpg?size=540x641"></p><p>两大男神的会面:崔始源和昌珉，明眸皓齿。</p><p><img src="http://p35.qhimg.com/t0165fb1a5bc9e8caa7.jpg?size=400x500"></p><p>从建国大业里的国军副官<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E4%BF%9E%E6%B5%8E%E6%97%B6&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">俞济时</a>到建党伟业里的<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E8%94%A1%E9%94%B7%E5%B0%86%E5%86%9B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">蔡锷将军</a>，刘德华一如既往地喜欢扮帅。</p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t01f4c67e26929c0496.jpg?size=500x543"></p><p>陈道明在<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《建国大业》</a>里扮演国民党时期上海警备司令部高官<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E9%98%8E%E9%94%A6%E6%96%87&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">阎锦文</a></p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t017f57cc0e3d25c82e.jpg?size=500x525"></p><p class="img-title">杨洋本来就是解放军艺术学院的学生</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t010c634de095677b13.jpg?size=500x491"></p><p class="img-title">梁朝伟香港飞虎队造型</p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t0195c58d4d3d2d882b.jpg?size=500x602"></p><p class="img-title">任贤齐的迷彩军装造型</p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t01cadc2ab95fcffb5c.jpg?size=500x752"></p><p class="img-title">陆毅</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01d1815838aeeafad6.jpg?size=500x335"></p><p><a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E9%9C%8D%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%8E&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">霍建华</a></p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01491ad6dbea7fd51d.jpg?size=500x665"></p><p>朱亚文在《远去的飞鹰》中饰演“飞鹰队”队长</p><p><img src="http://p35.qhimg.com/t015df11fdd595c943b.jpg?size=500x281"></p><p>佟大为在<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%81%E9%80%81%E7%BA%A2%E5%86%9B%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《十送红军》</a>中饰演红军战士张二光</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t0137fa78062fb55cd9.jpg?size=500x668"></p><p>孙红雷在<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E4%BA%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93%E6%98%AF%E6%B2%A7%E6%A1%91%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《人间正道是沧桑》</a>里饰演杨立青</p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t01e3a9f2799d2c3e7e.jpg?size=500x638"></p><p>姜文在《建国大业》中饰演国民党军统头子毛人凤</p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t01bf16889d11f99ca9.jpg?size=500x333"></p><p>郭涛在<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E7%88%B1%E6%83%85%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《父母爱情》</a>中饰演江德福</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t0123305421092a6d05.jpg?size=500x333"></p><p class="img-title">黄志忠的军装造型</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t010caba830c165d189.jpg?size=500x333"></p><p>邓超在<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E5%83%8F%E8%8A%B1%E5%84%BF%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《幸福像花儿一样》</a>里饰演白杨</p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t01fd452991d98bb448.jpg?size=400x500"></p><p>作为内地新生代的男一号，黄晓明用“演技”告诉你该怎么装才能装成硬汉。</p><p><img src="http://p35.qhimg.com/t01a69be3171b6ccd93.jpg?size=400x600"></p><p><a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E5%90%B4%E4%BA%A6%E5%87%A1&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">吴亦凡</a>军装，帅爆!</p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://jx.people.com.cn/n2/2016/0315/c190301-27941284-24.html">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='4624c2d25a14556340c89280fc413f7d'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>李易峰</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%93%E5%B3%B0&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=5&amp;m=9f830b78dddc126fb76866d7b7920b03052b42a2&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fjx.people.com.cn%2Fn2%2F2016%2F0315%2Fc190301-27941284-24.html" data-pos="1"> 宋仲基吴亦凡<b>李易峰</b>霍建华 中韩男星军装PK谁最帅 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%93%E5%B3%B0&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=6&amp;m=acaac931247c8aa35ffe0e95b151d5f4afdbd877&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnews.chinadaily.com.cn%2F2016-03%2F15%2Fcontent_23874304_3.htm" data-pos="2"> 林允刘亦菲<b>李易峰</b>刘诗诗汪涵 明星接地气本名让人哭笑不得 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%93%E5%B3%B0&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=7&amp;m=205aefb6dab3712dc36030b91c4bf12b7b0e32d2&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fjiangsu.china.com.cn%2Fhtml%2Fent%2Fhot%2F4775433_1.html" data-pos="3"> 鹿晗吴亦凡<b>李易峰</b> 男星萌照PK你家男神萌or傻 </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div class=mask style="display:none"></div> <div class="open-in-browser-tip" style="display:none"> <p>好无奈，微信君不让直接下载，别担心，点击<b>右上角</b>，选择“<b>在浏览器中打开</b>”就能下载啦~</p> <a class=close href="javascript:;"><img src="http://p3.qhimg.com/d/inn/a8960a66/close.png"></a> </div><script>(function(){var e=document.getElementById("news-body"